26.title: Me and J.R.
26.plot: Marty Stuart hosts a tribute to his late friend, Johnny Cash. Marty and his guests discuss the impact Johnny had on their lives and careers. Performances of songs Johnny wrote by Marty and his band, The Fabulous Superlatives, are featured along with several videos of Marty and Johnny playing together.
